        <div class="msgSubject">Gladiator 101</div>
        <div class="sm notbold">
          
          Posted: 2010-10-03 23:20:16 | Edited: Oct 24 2010  4:05pm  | <input type="checkbox" name="quote-128616961642549340" id="quote-128616961642549340" class="msgQuoteCheck" onchange="multiQuote2()"/><label for="quote-128616961642549340" onclick="multiQuote2()"> Quote</label>  | <a href="/forum.html?forum=175&amp;mid=128616961642549340&amp;post=1&amp;replyto=128616961642549340&amp;page=1" class="icon-replytothis" rel="nofollow">Reply to Post</a> | <a id="FOLLOW_MID_128616961642549340" onclick="followToggle('add','128616961642549340')" href="javascript:" class="icon-follow">Follow</a> 
