      <div class="msgContentFrame">Nice guide. <br /> <br />But is this guide for group players or also solo players (i think grouping)? Because for a gladiator in a group is tanking most important. But if you solo then i would suggest putting more points in STR and less in DEX. You have skills like Still Precision that increase accuracy. <br /> <br />Aegis Boon is a must have but use it wise! Especially when soloing or when you are in trouble. I use it most of the time when HP is low and i HAVE to heal myself with a healing skill like cure. It is also a good skill when you want to build up more TP without getting hit too often. Also fun when using against a group of mobs. Free healing :-D <br /> <br /><i><span class="sm">Edited, Oct 11th 2010  8:51am by grazypanda </span></i><div class="msgSig"><div class="msgSigBar sm">----------------------------</div>&lt;FONT size=&quot;11px&quot; face=&quot;Georgia&quot; color=&quot;#66666&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;Name:&lt;/b&gt; Aihredhiel Urdrenn &lt;b&gt;Starting City:&lt;/b&gt; Ul'dah &lt;b&gt;Physical Level:&lt;/b&gt; 36 &lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;GLA:&lt;/b&gt; 19 &lt;b&gt;CON:&lt;/b&gt; 16 &lt;b&gt;BSM:&lt;/b&gt; 19 &lt;b&gt;ARM:&lt;/b&gt; 19 &lt;b&gt;TAN:&lt;/b&gt; 16 &lt;b&gt;WVR:&lt;/b&gt; 17 &lt;b&gt;CRP:/&lt;b&gt; 12 &lt;b&gt;GLD:&lt;/b&gt; 14 &lt;b&gt;ALC:&lt;/b&gt; 16 &lt;b&gt;CUL:&lt;/b&gt; 9 &lt;b&gt;MIN:&lt;/b&gt; 15 &lt;b/&gt;BTN:&lt;/b&gt; 12 &lt;b&gt;FSH:&lt;/b&gt; 8&lt;/font&gt;</div></div>
